        <title>SPEEDOMETER/TACHOMETER MODULE LIGHT BULBS</title>
        <para>The illumination and Hi-beam indicator light bulbs fit into connectors that snap into the back of the
            speedometer/tachometer housing. The bulbs are accessed by tilting the speedometer/tachometer panel out as
            described in
